# Student UI System

All student-facing pages share a consistent shell and visual language.

## Layout Shell

Every protected student page renders inside `StudentDashboardLayout`:
- **Left sidebar** (231px, white, `StudentSidebar`) — logo, 3 nav items: Tổng quan, Lịch sử bài thi, Chứng chỉ
- **Top header** (`StudentHeader`) — sticky, avatar + name + email dropdown with logout
- **Content area** — `bg-[#E8F4FF]`, scrollable

Admin pages use `AdminDashboardLayout` (navy sidebar). The protected layout (`src/app/(protected)/layout.tsx`) switches automatically by role.

## Color Tokens (use Tailwind tokens, not raw hex)

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `text-main` / `bg-main` | #003562 | Primary navy — headings, buttons, sidebar active (admin) |
| `text-safety-orange` | #FF6A00 | Sidebar active state (student), accents |
| `text-semantic-info` / `bg-semantic-info` | #0EA5E9 | Info badges, links |
| `bg-[#E8F4FF]` | — | Page background (all protected pages) |
| `bg-[#FFF1E6]` | — | Student sidebar active bg |

Always use `bg-main` instead of `bg-[#003562]`, `text-safety-orange` instead of `text-[#FF6A00]`, etc.

## Card Pattern

All content cards use:
```
rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm
```

Avoid `shadow-md` or `shadow-lg` on content cards — keep them subtle (`shadow-sm`).

## Student Page Templates

### Dashboard (`/dashboard`)
1. `StudentProfileCard` — avatar, name, MSSV, faculty, CTA button
2. `StudentStatsRow` — 3-column grid: score, level, attempts
3. `StudentRadarChart` — competency radar + progress bars

### Exam Intro (`/exam`)
- Centered white card (`max-w-lg rounded-3xl`) over decorative ellipse bg
- Title (bold navy uppercase), description, info table (border rounded), start button

### Exam Taking (`/exam/[id]/take`)
- Full-screen with sticky timer, progress bar, one question per screen, bottom nav buttons

## Typography

- Page/card titles: `text-xl font-bold text-gray-900` or `text-main`
- Subtitles/labels: `text-sm text-gray-500`
- Stat values: `text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900`
- Body text: `text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500`

## Buttons

- Primary: `bg-main text-white hover:bg-[#002244] rounded-xl h-11 or h-12`
- With icon: add `gap-2` and Lucide icon at 16px (`h-4 w-4`)
